{"id":32,"parent_id":0,"book_id":80,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":32,"title":"Chapter 29: Alma Teaches about Faith and the Word of God","subtitle":"","short_title":"Chapter 29","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-29-alma-teaches-about-faith-and-the-word-of-god","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"chapter","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-29-alma-teaches-about-faith-and-the-word-of-god"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-29-alma-teaches-about-faith-and-the-word-of-god.head1"},[".titleNumber","Chapter 29"],["h1","Alma Teaches about Faith and the Word of God"]],[".bodyBlock",[".image",{"id":"f1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-29-alma-teaches-about-faith-and-the-word-of-god.f1"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_032_01.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-29-alma-teaches-about-faith-and-the-word-of-god.p3"},"Alma taught the Zoramites about faith. He said those people who ask for a sign before they will believe do not have faith."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-29-alma-teaches-about-faith-and-the-word-of-god.p4"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/32.17-18"},"Alma 32:17–18"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f2","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-29-alma-teaches-about-faith-and-the-word-of-god.f2"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_032_02.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-29-alma-teaches-about-faith-and-the-word-of-god.p5"},"Alma said faith is believing that something is true without actually being there to see it."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-29-alma-teaches-about-faith-and-the-word-of-god.p6"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/32.21"},"Alma 32:21"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-29-alma-teaches-about-faith-and-the-word-of-god.f3"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_032_03.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-29-alma-teaches-about-faith-and-the-word-of-god.p7"},"He explained that faith grows as a person wants to believe and listens to the word of God. The word is then planted in the person’s heart, and like a seed it starts to grow."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-29-alma-teaches-about-faith-and-the-word-of-god.p8"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/32.27-28"},"Alma 32:27–28"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-29-alma-teaches-about-faith-and-the-word-of-god.f4"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_032_04.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-29-alma-teaches-about-faith-and-the-word-of-god.p9"},"As a person learns more about the gospel, the seed sprouts and keeps growing. The person knows that the seed is good, and his or her faith grows stronger."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-29-alma-teaches-about-faith-and-the-word-of-god.p10"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/32.30"},"Alma 32:30"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-29-alma-teaches-about-faith-and-the-word-of-god.f5"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_032_05.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-29-alma-teaches-about-faith-and-the-word-of-god.p11"},"Alma said that just as a good seed produces good fruit, the word of God brings blessings to people who have faith."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-29-alma-teaches-about-faith-and-the-word-of-god.p12"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/32.31,41-43"},"Alma 32:31, 41–43"]]]]]]]],"refs":null}
